OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,FAndy Burnham said he will "offer new
OL,7,Fopportunities to extend devolution"
OL,8,Fhere in Wales if he becomes prime
OL,9,Fminister but suggested that would mean
OL,10,Fmore local decision-making, not
OL,11,Fnecessarily more power for the Welsh
OL,12,FGovernment.
OL,14,FIt's a mixed message for the Plaid
OL,15,FCymru first minister who said he'll
OL,16,Fcontinue to make "the same positive
OL,17,Fcase" for a change to Welsh
OL,18,Fdevolution, but who is warning that Mr
OL,19,FBurnham's main pledge "will mean very
OL,20,Flittle to the people of Wales".
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@cO]xD@ROUyD@EO]{D@WOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/13
