PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,FIt was reported last week that the
OL,7,Flikely next prime minister does not
OL,8,Fintend to change the way that Wales
OL,9,Fand Scotland are funded, the mechanism
OL,10,Fknown as the Barnett Formula, if he
OL,11,Fmoves into Number 10.
OL,13,FThat's at odds with previous comments
OL,14,Fof his during his time as Greater
OL,15,FManchester mayor reported by the
OL,16,FNational newspaper. He previously said
OL,17,Fhe wanted to "tear up" the funding
OL,18,Fmodel and even earlier, during the
OL,19,FLabour leadership campaign of 2015,
OL,20,Fmade comments acknowledging that the
OL,21,FBarnett Formula was unfair to Wales.
OL,26,@yD@NOUyD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
