PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,FThe First Minister called that
OL,7,F"disappointing" while a spokesperson
OL,8,Ffor Mr Burnham said that he "will put
OL,9,FWales at the centre of any government
OL,10,Fhe runs, radically pushing power down
OL,11,Fand out of Westminster and Whitehall".
OL,13,FReform UK is now the second largest
OL,14,Fparty in the Senedd.
OL,16,FIts leader, Dan Thomas, said: "The
OL,17,Fpeople of Wales and the wider United
OL,18,FKingdom did not vote for more
OL,19,Fconstitutional change or another round
OL,20,Fof devolution debates.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]pD@]OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,F"The British people were not given the
OL,7,Fopportunity to choose Andy Burnham as
OL,8,Fprime minister. If he intends to
OL,9,Fpursue a fundamentally different
OL,10,Fagenda, including further devolution,
OL,11,Fhe should return to the people and
OL,12,Fseek a fresh mandate.
OL,14,F"Reform believes the public, not
OL,15,Fpoliticians behind closed doors,
OL,16,Fshould decide who governs this country
OL,17,Fand what policies they should pursue.
OL,18,FThat is why we are calling for a
OL,19,FGeneral Election."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
