CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,FDarren Millar, the leader of the Welsh
OL,7,FConservatives in the Senedd was also
OL,8,Fcritical, stating: "Andy Burnham is
OL,9,Fmaking the same mistakes as Keir
OL,10,FStarmer, set to become Prime Minister
OL,11,Fof one of the world's largest
OL,12,Feconomies without a plan to govern.
OL,14,F"Without a plan, he can't take the
OL,15,Ftough decisions to cut taxes, reduce
OL,16,Fwelfare, grow our economy, deliver
OL,17,Fenergy security and invest in defence.
OL,26,@pD@TOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
