PN,43611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,F"Instead of growing our economy, Andy
OL,7,FBurnham's main commitment seems to be
OL,8,Fmoving powers around between
OL,9,Fpoliticians.
OL,11,F"It's increasingly clear that Kemi
OL,12,FBadenoch is the only party leader with
OL,13,Fa plan to get Britain working."
OL,15,FThe Liberal Democrats weren't
OL,16,Fimpressed with today's speech either.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
