PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,FWelsh Lib Dem MP David Chadwick said:
OL,7,F"Andy Burnham says he wants to take
OL,8,Fpower out of Westminster, yet today's
OL,9,Fplans appear to leave Wales once again
OL,10,Fat the back of the queue compared to
OL,11,FEnglish regions.
OL,13,F"If Labour can find the ambition to
OL,14,Fdevolve powers across England, they
OL,15,Fshould have the ambition to give Wales
OL,16,Fthe same powers as Scotland.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
