PN,43613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1782904686
OL,3,CAndy Burnham promises 'opportunities
OL,4,Cto extend devolution' for Wales
OL,6,F"The Welsh Liberal Democrats believe
OL,7,FWales deserves a stronger devolution
OL,8,Fsettlement, starting with the powers
OL,9,Fthat will make the biggest difference
OL,10,Fto people's lives and our economy:
OL,11,Fgreater borrowing and taxation powers,
OL,12,Fthe devolution of rail and the Crown
OL,13,FEstate, and a fair funding formula for
OL,14,FWales."
OL,16,FIn his speech, Andy Burnham said that
OL,17,Fhe would "reach out" to other parties
OL,18,Fto create a "greater sense of unity"
OL,19,Facross the UK. Reaching out to some of
OL,20,Fthe parties here in Wales may pose
OL,21,Fmore of a challenge to that aim.
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@TO]zD@MOUzD@dO]
